classes.name: AffineTransform
classes.description: Represents a 2D affine transformation that performs a linear mapping from 2D coordinates to other 2D coordinates, preserving the straightness and parallelism of lines. Used in Ignition Vision for rotating, scaling, translating, and shearing custom drawn shapes.

params.name: m11

fields.name: TYPE_IDENTITY
fields.description: This constant indicates that the transform defined by this object is an identity transform (0).

fields.name: TYPE_TRANSLATION
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a translation (1).

fields.name: TYPE_UNIFORM_SCALE
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a uniform scale (2).

fields.name: TYPE_GENERAL_SCALE
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a general scale (4).

fields.name: TYPE_MASK_SCALE
fields.description: This constant is a bit mask for any of the scale flag bits (6).

fields.name: TYPE_FLIP
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a mirror image flip (64).

fields.name: TYPE_QUADRANT_ROTATION
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a quadrant rotation (8).

fields.name: TYPE_GENERAL_ROTATION
fields.description: This flag bit indicates that the transform defined by this object performs a rotation by an arbitrary angle (16).

fields.name: TYPE_MASK_ROTATION
fields.description: This constant is a bit mask for any of the rotation flag bits (24).

fields.name: TYPE_GENERAL_TRANSFORM
fields.description: This constant indicates that the transform defined by this object performs an arbitrary conversion of the input coordinates (32).

fields.name: OPEN
fields.description: The closure type for an open arc with no path segments connecting the two ends of the arc segment (0).

fields.name: CHORD
fields.description: The closure type for an arc closed by drawing a straight line segment from the start of the arc segment to the end of the arc segment (1).

fields.name: PIE
fields.description: The closure type for an arc closed by drawing straight line segments from the start and end of the arc segment to the center of the full ellipse (2).
